proxy_args - Same args passed to socksocket.set_proxy() if present.\ntimeout - Optional socket timeout value, in seconds.\nsource_address - tuple (host, port) for the socket to bind to as its source\naddress before connecting (only for compatibility)"]}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.wrapmodule", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "module", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["wrapmodule(module)\nAttempts to replace a module's socket library with a SOCKS socket.\nThis will only work on modules that import socket directly into the\nnamespace."]}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.__make_proxy_chain", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.DebugPrint", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "text", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.Main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.DEBUG", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.HAVE_SSL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.HAVE_PYOPENSSL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.TLS_CA_CERTS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.HAVE_SSL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.SSL.SSLv23_METHOD", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.PROXY_TYPE_DEFAULT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.PROXY_TYPE_NONE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.PROXY_TYPE_SOCKS4", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_chain.chained_socks.PROXY_TYPE_SOCKS5", "type": null, "documentation"